perform periodic physical inventory of supplies or property and prepare and submit a copy of the Report of the Physical Count of Inventories to the Office of the Auditor; and

GSO and Municipal Accountant to regularly conduct reconciliation of their reports so that any discrepancy noted could promptly adjusted and reconciled.

We recommended that the Local Chief Executive require the:

