Municipal Accountant to review and reconcile the discrepancy noted on the balances of the PPE account as reported in the Statement of Financial Position as against the corresponding schedules, to fairly present the Financial Statements;

Municipal Accountant and the General Services Officer to:
regularly conduct reconciliation of their reports so that any discrepancy noted could promptly adjusted and reconciled; and
maintain the required Property, Plant and Equipment Ledger Cards, Real Property Ledger Cards and Property Cards, respectively.

