Exert all efforts for the collection of the receivables;
Reconcile and analyze the accounts to determine whether they warrant adjustment or write-off in accordance with existing COA rules and regulations;
Furnish certification and/or reasons why the books of accounts/records/financial statements/schedules and supporting documents cannot be located; and
Require proper turn-over of documents/pending work from officials and employees retiring/separating from office/service to ensure completeness of records.

